Package: viord
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian inference in cumulative regression models
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-11-02
Authors@R: person("Emanuele", "Aliverti", role = c("aut", "cre"), email
        = "aliverti@stat.unipd.it")
Description: Provides tools for approximate Bayesian inference in cumulative probit regression models, implemented via Expectation Propagation (EP) and Variational Bayes algorithms under mean-field or partially factorized mean-field assumptions; see Aliverti (2025) <arXiv:2511.06967> for details.
